<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <% include partials/head %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include partials/header %>

    <section class="parallax-window parallax-window--trading-payment">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>Trading instruments</h2>
            <p>Here you will find an overview of the Forex trading instruments available to our clients. We offer our clients access to the Forex market, as well as opportunities to trade gold and silver. This list is constantly complemented in order to improve the terms of trade.</p>
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
              <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Trading</a></li>
              <li class="active">Payment</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="trading container ptl pbl">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <h4 class="headtitle">Open <b>account!</b></h4>
          <div class="seperator seperator--full mbl"><i class="icons icons--seperator"></i></div>
          <p class="contens">Both Euros and Dollars can be transfered to the trading account by using different payment solutions provided by our company. Once any financial resources are transfered to the trading account, it will immediately become active. The currency you transfered to the account may differ from the base currency of the account. In such cases, our financial department converts the transfered funds using the exchange rate of the central bank and transfers the resources to your account according to the base currency you have chosen. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="trading trading-step">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <ul class="trading-step--list">
              <li class="trading-step__item">
                <span class="trading-step__icons"><i class="icons icons-trading--opening"></i></span>
                <span class="trading-step__label">Account opening</span>
              </li>
              <li class="trading-step__item">
                <span class="trading-step__icons"><i class="icons icons-trading--deposit"></i></span>
                <span class="trading-step__label">Funds deposit</span>
              </li>
              <li class="trading-step__item">
                <span class="trading-step__icons"><i class="icons icons-trading--trading-open"></i></span>
                <span class="trading-step__label">Trading</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="trading trading-registration trading-payment-table">
      <div class="container ptl pbl">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h4 class="headtitle">prediction</h4>
            <div class="seperator seperator--full mbl"><i class="icons icons--seperator"></i></div>
            <% include components/trading-table-payment %>
            <p>Attention! Because of our support for the fight against money laundering and funding of international terrorism, Adamant Finance does not accept payments from nor make payments to any third parties. Financial transactions can only take place between our company and the owner of the account.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
      

    <% include partials/footer-without-contest %>

    <% include partials/scripts %>
  </body>
</html>